<section id="why" style="pmo-why">
  <title>Why Mallard?</title>
  <list>
    <item><p>Mallard helps you write small and focused topics, making it easier
    for your users to find the information they need quickly.</p></item>
    <item><p>Mallard is simple.  New and experienced writers alike find Mallard
    provides the right level of abstraction so they can focus on better
    content.</p></item>
    <item><p>Mallard documents are designed to be extended.  You can easily add
    content for plugins or added functionality without modifying the original
    sources.</p></item>
  </list>
</section>

